<h1>${title}</h1>

<p>
EurocarbDB is an EU-funded initiative for the creation of software and 
standards for the systematic collection of carbohydrate structures 
and their experimental data. Initially, only mass-spectrometry, HPLC and 
NMR data is accepted, however EurocarbDB is an actively developed 
<a href="http://eurocarb.googlecode.com">open source project</a>, and 
additional techniques may be supported in the future.
</p>
<p>
In addition to a central database of carbohydrate structures and experimental data,
EurocarbDB also includes a suite of various <a href="tools.action">tools</a>.
</p>

